Package MOBLIMA.dataStructure

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
MOBLIMA.dataStructure.Movie
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Movie extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a Movie that can be screened at a cinema. Each movie has configurable attributes.
